刚果首都音乐会发生踩踏事故 九人死亡https://www.nme.com/news/music/nine-killed-in-stampede-at-concert-in-congos-capital-3779948?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nine-killed-in-stampede-at-刚果首都音乐会Daniel PetersThu, 01 Aug 2024 07:45:44 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3779948 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="迈克·卡兰贝烈士体育场" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>由刚果福音歌手迈克·卡兰贝 (Mike Kalambay) 主持的活动</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nine-killed-in-stampede-at-concert-in-congos-capital-3779948">《九号邮报》在刚果首都演唱会发生踩踏事故中丧生的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="迈克·卡兰贝烈士体育场" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/MartyrStadium-Congo-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>刚果首都<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-shares-support-for-palestine-sudan-dr-congo-and-college-protests-we-aint-free-til-we-all-free-3756245">金沙萨</a>，刚果福音歌手迈克·卡兰贝 (Mike Kalambay) 举行音乐会时发生踩踏事件，造成 9 人死亡。</p><p>这起悲惨事件于上周六（7 月 27 日）在可容纳 8 万人的烈士体育场发生。据<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c06km73rzzyo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>报道，活动现场拍摄的照片显示，会场人满为患。</p><p>金沙萨州长丹尼尔·邦巴在一份新闻声明中将这一事件归咎于“过度行为和人群流动”。据当地媒体<em>BBC</em>报道，其中一名受害者是一名 10 岁的儿童。该活动还在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mr6brvI8jeA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>上进行了直播。</p><p>音乐会组织者Maajabu Gospel周日（7月28日）发表声明，对遇难者表示遗憾和悲伤。他们补充说，活动中的“麻烦制造者”应对此负责，活动现场有 2000 名警察试图平息骚乱。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C98KOk0MFPe/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.4