ing="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PostMalone-F1-Trillion-tracklist-Tim-McGraw-Dolly-Parton.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PostMalone-F1-Trillion-tracklist-Tim-McGraw-Dolly-Parton-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PostMalone-F1-Trillion-tracklist-Tim-McGraw-Dolly-Parton-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PostMalone-F1-Trillion-tracklist-Tim-McGraw-Dolly-Parton-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PostMalone-F1-Trillion-tracklist-Tim-McGraw-Dolly-Parton-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/PostMalone-F1-Trillion-tracklist-Tim-McGraw-Dolly-Parton-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone)</a>公布了他的新专辑《F-1 Trillion》的完整曲目列表，特邀嘉宾包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">蒂姆·麦格劳 (Tim McGraw)</a> 。看看下面。</p><p>这位艺术家的真名是 Austin Richard Post，将于 8 月 16 日发行他的乡村风格第六张录音室唱片<a href="https://posty.lnk.to/f-1trillion" target="_blank" rel="noopener">。您可以在此处预订/预保存</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/post-malone-austin-review-3474831">波斯特·马龙——《奥斯汀》评论：波斯蒂诚实地讲述了他的恶习</a></strong></li></ul><p>Posty 已经预览了该项目的“Pour Me A Drink”（壮举 Blake Shelton）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-and-morgan-wallen-announce-joint-single-i-had-some-help-3753544">“I Had Some Help”（壮举 Morgan Wallen）</a>和“Guy For That”（壮举<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luke-combs">Luke Combs</a> ）。 5月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-teases-new-song-while-performing-at-academy-of-country-music-awards-3757268">他在乡村音乐奖表演时首次推出了《Never Love You Again》</a> 。</p><p>现在，这位明星公布了“F-1 Trillion”的完整 18 首歌曲曲目列表，该歌曲拥有与一些最伟大的乡村音乐家的合作。</p><p>这张密纹唱片以麦格劳合作的《Wrong Ones》开场，之后是与帕顿合作的《Have The Heart》。</p><p>此外，Posty 还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-stapleton">Chris Stapleton</a> （《California Sober》）、Hank Williams Jr.（《Finer Things》）、Brad Paisley（《Goes Without Saying》）、Lainey Wilson（《Nosedive》）和 Sierra 等人联手费雷尔（《不再爱你》）。</p><p>请参阅下面的公告帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-F-ucwM3yy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 