m/news/tv/squid-game-renewed-third-final-season-ahead-season-two-premiere-3779898">《鱿鱼游戏》第二季的发布日期已确定，续订第三季和最后一季，</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
